        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You adapt to new hierarchies with ease and find reassurance in a reliable command structure. When using the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Follow the Expert] activity in exploration mode, you gain a +3 circumstance bonus if the ally you're following is an expert and a +4 circumstance bonus if your ally is a master. In addition, if you roll a success on your saving throw against a mental effect that would make you controlled, you get a critical success instead.</p>"
